islike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T06:56:22.000Z","msg":"［置頂行動］請改用網上遊行避免送頭<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2062449\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2062449</a>"},{"pid":"48298c8a0f284c4f5ff61f027d854d5d1c88a521","tid":2063480,"uid":336429,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f38b2a80ba2fd91a68d5ec5a8539b666eceed892","tid":2063480,"uid":13138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T04:45:53.000Z","msg":"上到岸你已經續漸減弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你點對得住生你出黎嘅低氣壓？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你點對得住星期日要返工嘅香港人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地屌曬你老母！依家係咪已經吹爆咗香港啦？8號風球達成咗啦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果依個post咁都上唔到熱門，我正式宣布依個風球玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T06:57:55.000Z","msg":"核彈,收到風有外國勢力登陸澳門,手足要推上熱門搞大佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebc1c00043f389d9b5333ac91e15574e0a12092a","tid":2063480,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T07:27:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UngcVHa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUngcVHa.jpg&h=5afe454d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1️⃣香港白領(行政及文職)同行工會<br />\n總之你係返office 工都基本上合符入資格（唔清楚自己入唔入到都可先pm問下工會先）<br />\n入會表：<a href=\"http://application.hkwccu.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fapplication.hkwccu.org&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJlcETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=6715d5a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://application.hkwccu.org</a><br />\n<br />\n2️⃣前線新力量零售工會<br />\n好簡單，做零售的手足都可入，不論你係全職定兼職都入得<br />\n入會表：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Y5UiR9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Y5UiR9&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJlcETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=9b6e8192\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Y5UiR9</a><br />\n<br />\n3️⃣飲食及酒店業職工總會<br />\n都係好簡單，做飲食的手足都可入，你係學生炒下散又好，全職定兼職都入得<br />\n入會表：<a href=\"https://forms.gle/8yK7ZEtZboY45apU7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2F8yK7ZEtZboY45apU7&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJlcETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=bbcb5fde\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/8yK7ZEtZboY45apU7</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">入會機會黎喇 <br />\n大學生及兼職打工仔</span></span><br />\n個幾星期 工會人數增長都係得千幾人<br />\n大家踴躍入會 齊齊投票<br />\n入左會先可以公投<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">[要人] 620反國安法罷工罷課公投<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2063531\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2063531</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></div>"},{"pid":"3bbca838b3bb309de74378b832c28086614bcf26","tid":2063480,"uid":13138,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"607f479dfb8ca1f155f8580c3f0d4b5c6acc7090","tid":2063480,"uid":7323,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T06:55:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">死尻雀，屌你老母啊</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T07:32:24.000Z","msg":"朝早啲古菇固仲大聲過佢"},{"pid":"1a4c93f760a6c851c138c8b56ffcb9b76c91f152","tid":2063480,"uid":137725,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T07:37:26.000Z","msg":"要人！！！！！！！！"},{"pid":"f7e3e45923421938bc0c58602c045e1cbfda8ff9","tid":2063480,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a4c93f760a6c851c138c8b56ffcb9b76c91f152","tid":2063480,"uid":137725,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T07